history.content:
160 + 170 is fine, 161, 168, 122, 120 (last one assuming taken prereqs already) all also would be pretty good with 170.

126 (its probability, not really EE and applicable to 188/189) or 162 would be rough but also doable assuming 170 only other technical. 189+170 is also good if you have experience with probability greater than cs70 (like ee126, stat 134 etc)...

there are overall a lot of options... pretty much anything other than 172, 176 maybe 174 sounds okay given only 2 upper divs.
